data.description: Welcome home to 9001 Jefferies Ave! This 3 bedroom Cape Code offers plenty of room to enjoy and entertain. Updates include new carpet in the bedrooms. An updated bathroom with shower, new cabinet and lighting is also located on the first floor. There is an enclosed porch off of the kitchen for relaxation.  The large bedroom upstairs has an attached finished room which could be used as a large walk-in closet, small office or playroom. The partially finished basement includes a newly created rec room. Additional renovations include complete interior painting (2023), new carpeting (2023), kitchen upgrades (2023), and a newer furnace (2022). All appliances stay and a home warranty is included for added peace of mind! Schedule your showing and come make this home yours today!!
